'''全球飢餓指數'''（GHI）是一個多層面的統計工具，用於描述國家的[[飢餓|飢餓]]狀況。可利用GHI評估全球對抗飢餓方面的進步和失敗。<ref name="bbc">{{cite news |url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/8306556.stm |title= Global hunger worsening, warns UN |publisher= [[BBC|BBC]] (Europe) |date= 2009-10-14 |accessdate= 2010-08-22 |archive-date= 2018-10-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181023054023/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/8306556.stm |dead-url= no }}</ref>GHI每年更新一次。

該指數由[[國際糧食政策研究所|國際糧食政策研究所]]（IFPRI）採納和進一步發展，並於2006年首次在德國[[非營利組織|非營利組織]]（NGO）[[救济世界饥饿组织|救济世界饥饿组织]]（Welthungerhilfe）發表。2007年以來，愛爾蘭非政府組織{{tsl|en|Concern Worldwide|關注世界}}作為共同發行人加入團體。<ref name="GHI2006">IFPRI/ Welthungerhilfe: [http://www.ifpri.org/sites/default/files/publications/ghi06.pdf The Challenge of Hunger − Global Hunger Index: Facts, determinants, and trends. Case studies of post conflict countries of Afghanistan and Sierra Leone] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ifpri.org/sites/default/files/publications/ghi06.pdf |date=20130430083605 }}. Bonn, October 2006.</ref><ref name="GHI2007">IFPRI/ Concern/ Welthungerhilfe: [http://www.ifpri.org/sites/default/files/publications/pubs_pubs_cp_ghi07.pdf The Challenge of Hunger 2007 − Global Hunger Index: Facts, determinants, and trends 2007] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ifpri.org/sites/default/files/publications/pubs_pubs_cp_ghi07.pdf |date=20131117010709 }}. Measures being taken to reduce acute undernourishment and chronic hunger. Bonn, October 2007.</ref><ref name="GHI2008">IFPRI/ Concern/ Welthungerhilfe: [http://www.ifpri.org/sites/default/files/publications/ghi08.pdf Global Hunger Index − The Challenge of Hunger 2008] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ifpri.org/sites/default/files/publications/ghi08.pdf |date=20130131120021 }}. Bonn, Washington D.C., Dublin. October 2008.</ref><ref name="GHI2009">IFPRI/ Concern/ Welthungerhilfe: [http://www.ifpri.org/sites/default/files/publications/ghi09.pdf 2009 Global Hunger Index − The Challenge of Hunger: Focus on Financial Crisis and Gender Inequality] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ifpri.org/sites/default/files/publications/ghi09.pdf |date=20140903040440 }}. Bonn, Washington D. C., Dublin. October 2009.</ref>

在2009年，GHI對121個[[發展中國家|發展中國家]]和[[轉型期國家|轉型期國家]]進行了計算，其中84位進入排名。GHI的報告每年聚焦於一個主要的主題：在2009年，該指數衡量[[飢餓|飢餓]]與[[性別平等|性別平等]]之間的聯繫。<ref name="GHI-Summary2009">[http://www.ifpri.org/publication/2009-global-hunger-index 2009 Global Hunger Index - Summary] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ifpri.org/publication/2009-global-hunger-index |date=20190725001428 }}, IFPRI, Washington, DC</ref><ref name="CTA">{{Cite web |url=http://knowledge.cta.int/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/2009-global-hunger-index |title=Technical Center for Agriculture and Rural Cooperation (CTA), 2009 Global Hunger Index |access-date=2010-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130729051726/http://knowledge.cta.int/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/2009-global-hunger-index |archive-date=2013-07-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>此外，還對飢餓狀況對金融危機的影響進行了分析。在年度GHI之外，[[印度國家飢餓指數|印度國家飢餓指數]]（ISHI）於2008年發表<ref name="India-GHI2009">Menon, Purnima / Deolalikar, Anil / Bhaskar, Anjor: [http://www.ifpri.org/publication/comparisons-hunger-across-states-india-state-hunger-index India State Hunger Index (2009): Comparison of Hunger Across States] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ifpri.org/publication/comparisons-hunger-across-states-india-state-hunger-index |date=20150601142746 }}</ref>，以及衣索比亞次國家飢餓指數於2009年發表<ref name="Ethiopia-GHI2009">Schmidt, Emily / Dorosh, Paul (October 2009): [http://www.ifpri.org/publication/sub-national-hunger-index-ethiopia A Sub-National Index for Ethiopia: Assessing Progress in Region-Level Outcomes] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ifpri.org/publication/sub-national-hunger-index-ethiopia |date=20180930144225 }}. International Food Policy Research Institute (IFPRI) and Ethiopian Development Research Institute (EDRI): ESSP-II Discussion Paper 5.</ref>。

==指数的计算方式==

指数以百分制来衡量一个国家，其中0为最佳（“不存在饥饿”）100为最差（亦即分數越高，該國的食物狀況越差，儘管這兩個極端都不是在實踐中取得）。分數低於4.9表示「低飢餓」，分數在5至9.9之間表示「適度飢餓」，10至19.9之間表示「嚴重饥饿」，20至29.9之間表示「驚人」，而30以上表示「非常令人擔憂的」飢餓問題。

GHI包括三個同等分量的加權指標：
#營養不良者占人口的百分比；
#五歲以下體重不足兒童的發生率；
#五歲以下兒童的死亡率。<ref name="GHI2009"></ref>

2009年GHI使用的數據為2002至2007年期間，也就是最近獲得的GHI三個組成部分的全球數據。這些數據當中，營養不良的比例來自[[聯合國糧食及農業組織|聯合國糧食及農業組織]]，期間為2003年至2005年的数据。<ref name=FAO2008]>[http://www.fao.org/docrep/011/i0291e/i0291e00.htm State of food insecurity in the world 2008] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fao.org/docrep/011/i0291e/i0291e00.htm |date=20180613234142 }}. Food and Agriculture Organization. Rome, 2008.</ref>5歲以下兒童體重不足的數據是根據由[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]（WHO）<ref name="WHO">[http://www.who.int/nutgrowthdb/database/countries/en/index.html Global database on child growth and malnutrition] {{Wayback|url=http://www.who.int/nutgrowthdb/database/countries/en/index.html |date=20100927063801 }}. World Health Organization. Geneva, 2009.</ref>、[[聯合國兒童基金會|聯合國兒童基金會]]（UNICEF）<ref name="UNICEF2009a">United Nations Children’s Fund. 2009. The state of the world’s children 2009: maternal and newborn health. New York.</ref><ref name="UNICEF2009b">UNICEF. 2009b. [http://www.childinfo.org/undernutrition_underweight.php Childinfo statistics on child nutrition] {{Wayback|url=http://www.childinfo.org/undernutrition_underweight.php |date=20160304030031 }}. New York.</ref>和人口統計與健康調查（MEASURE DHS）<ref name="MDHS">MEASURE DHS. 2009. [http://www.measuredhs.com/aboutsurveys/dhs/start.cfm Demographic health surveys] {{Wayback|url=http://www.measuredhs.com/aboutsurveys/dhs/start.cfm |date=20100926155714 }}. Calverton, USA.</ref>根據收集到的在2002-07年期間最新資料和數據，而兒童死亡率是2007年兒童基金會的數據。2009年GHI和以新算法重新計算的1990年GHI，不能直接與舊算法的GHI值相比較。

